@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBackgroundColor #E8F4FA
skinparam classBorderColor #2C7DA0
[*] --> Delivered
Delivered --> Pending : process
Pending --> Created : update
Created --> Closed : reject
Closed --> Completed : review
Closed : entry / log housekeeping
Delivered --> Completed : revert
Completed --> [*]
@enduml